94th Street, east side, between Forty-sixth and Alstyne Avenues, showing 4 views of the Burroughs family burial place. View No. 1 also shows a factory at the S.W. corner of 94th Street and So. Railroad Avenue. Views two and three show Alstyne Avenue in the foreground and an old barn at the rear of the Card house. View No. four shows homes
on the north side of Forty-sixth Avenue.
May 1923
Views 1,2 3 and 4
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
